
1  “Ore kenya teina kata, Olaitoriani ojo, ore iloik loo laiguanak le Yuda, o loik loo lkituaak lenyena, o loik loo lapolosak, o loik loo loibonok le Nkai o loik le lelo oomanya Yerusalem neyauni aitung'uaa nkuraren enye; 
2  neidapashi ninche te dukuya enkolong o lapa, o lorora pooki le keper, naa ninche apa etonyorra ninche neisiaai, aa ninche apa etusujaitie, aa ninche eing'orutua neserem; nemeiturrurri ninche arashu enukari; netiu ninche anaa modiok ti oriong enkop. 
3  Kenyorrarri kenya keeya aaitudutie enkishui ilo pisiai oleku lele marei torrono too wuejitin pooki naterewa nanu ninche, Olaitoriani loo lororani ojo.

Engoki o enkitamioto


4  “Ijoki iyie ninche, nji ejo Olaitoriani, Amaa tenebatata oltung'ani aimeitoki ninye adumunye? Amaa teneibelekenya oltung'ani alo, aimeitoki ninye ashukunye? 
5  Kainyoo naa pee eibelekenyate kulo tung'ana aapuo aashuko siadi anaake? Neibung ninche aakurraki elejare, neany ninche eshukunye. 
6  Ainining'ishe nanu, kake eitu ninche eiro aaitorioki; meetae oltung'ani oirridu te ntorroni enye, ejo ‘Kainyoo nanu ataasa?’ Eibelekenyakino ake pooki ng'ae nkoitoi enyena, anaa embarta nakuetiki olarrabal. 
7  Ekeyiolo ninye entilagos te shumata nkatitin enyena; ore enturkuluo o emotoroki, o enkaileeri neibung nkatitin enye naapuonunye; kake meyiolo iltung'ana laainei nkitanapat Olaitoriani.


8  “Kaji intae inkoko tenijojo, ‘Kira iyiook ng'eni, ore enkitanapata O Laitoriani netii tenebo iyiook?’ Kake, ng'ura, ina alamu elejare oo lasirak ajo eitaa ninye emonkoi. 
9  Ore lelo tung'ana ng'eni naa keitukurruni, keidang'ieki ninche neyae; Oi, etanyaita ninche ororei lo Laitoriani, naa kaa ng'eno natii atua ninche? 
10   Neaku kaisho nanu nkituaak enye ilkulikae naisho nkurman enye lelo ooisulu, enkaraki naa ore ebaiki oloti ometabaiki olkitok eeta pooki ng'ae olorok le dupoto te nkoitoi elejare. Eiteru to loiboni le Nkai o metabaiki olapolosani ometabaiki olapolosani meetae ake ole measisho te lejare. 
11   Eishiunye ninche olbae loo ltung'ana laainei te nkitaakunoto ejo, ‘Eseriani, eseriani’, nemetii eseriani. 
12  Ketukurrutua ninche ina kata pee eas olminong A-a, eitu ninche ekurru tukul; menya ninche orere. Neaku kebatata ninche tiatua lelo ootabatatate; ore ake pee aitame nanu ninche, nenang'ari ninche, Olaitoriani ojo.


13  Ore tenajo aiturrur ninche; Olaitoriani ojo, nemetii ilng'anayio o sabibu arashu ilng'abolo olng'aboli etoito ninye mbenek, ore apa ina naishoo nanu ninche netulusoyie alo aing'uaa ninche.”


14  Kainyoo pee kitoni iyiook aaitirring'a enturrurroto tenebo, maape iyiook atua nena anas naasheta, pee kindak teine; amu etudung'oko iyiook Olaitoriani Enkai ang enkidaata, neishoo iyiook enkare natii esayiet matook, enkaraki nikitaasa iyiook eng'oki to Laitoriani. 
15  Kisiligu iyiook eseriani kake meetae esidai naewuo, enkata enkishiunoto, kake ng'ura, enkuretisho. 
16  “Ore enkikurrukur oo mbartan enye nening'o te wueji neji Dan. Ore to ltoilo loo mbartan enye e njore neikirikira enkop pooki. Kepuonu ninche aaidaikie enkop o pooki toki nabore, enkanasa o lelo oomanya atua. 
17  Amu ng'ura, kairriu nanu tiatua intae ilasuriaa o nturbubuani naata esayiet nemeibooyo intalengo, naa keony ninche intae.” Olaitoriani ojo.

Osina le Yeremia te nkaraki iltung'ana lenyena


18  Meishiunoyu osina lai?

kemuoi oltau lai.


19  Toning'o olkiyioi

le ntito oo ltung'ana laainei

eing'uaa enkadoro o endapasho enkop.

“Aimetii Olaitoriani atua Sion?

Aimetii olaiguanani lenye atua ninye?”

Kainyoo pee aaitagoro ninche too

nkitanyaanyukot enye naaguetuno,

o too nkitanyaanyukot enye omon?


20  “Etulusoyie enkisampuare;

eishunye enkata enkirowuaj,

neitu eitajeuni iyiook.”


21  Amu ore ilo bae leina tito

oo ltung'ana laainei naa oltau lai etipikaki olbae,

aishir nanu, naaiputa nanu enking'asia.


22  Aimetii olchani atua Gilead?

Aimetii olabaani ine?

Kainyoo naa pee eitu eshukuni

embiotisho eina tito oo ltung'ana laainei?

